      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRADMORE (4) was a last start winner (29.72) at Launceston who is building a strong winning record. Strike rate this course strong having won three of four tries. Won at his only start from this box. In sparkling form and looks the one to beat again. HEY JETT (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (30.59) at Launceston behind Fast Felix in a Grade 6. Hard to beat again. FIRE WATER BURN (3) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (25.95) from Box 2 at this track. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from five starts. Will give a great sight again. GOODNIGHT HEIDI (2) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
